                <h4>快速介绍</h4><ul><li>推箱子&amp;拉箱子合作游戏 <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/1027720/Push_Pull/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">Push Pull</a></li><li>C64 16位街机风格武士游戏 <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/1028300/Katana_Soul/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">Katana Soul</a></li><li>快节奏多人射击对战 <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/796430/SHiRO_011/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">SHiRO 011</a></li><li><a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/704270/Generation_Zero/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">零世代 Generation Zero</a></li><li>开放世界多人生存合作 <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/794260/Outward/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">Outward</a></li><li><a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/995240/RemiLore_Lost_Girl_in_the_Lands_of_Lore/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">RemiLore～少女と異世界と魔導書～</a></li><li>NEXT Studios 新作 <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/942970/Unheard/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">疑案追声 Unheard</a></li><li>育碧的 VR 街机射击游戏 <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/647590/Space_Junkies/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">Space Junkies™</a></li><li><a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/813300/CODE_CRACKER/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">CODE CRACKER 代码破译者</a></li><li>免费水彩+简笔画风格点击游戏<a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/1036200/Song_Animals/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">Song Animals</a></li><li><a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/1044770/Goddess_of_Math/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">Goddess of Math 数学女神</a></li><li>像素点击策略塔防 <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/1044170/Lord_of_the_click/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">Lord of the click</a></li><li>台湾动作冒险游戏 <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/911220/Dusk_Diver/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">Dusk Diver 酉閃町</a></li><li>90年代风的网格导向 RPG <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/873890/Legends_of_Amberland_The_Forgotten_Crown/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">Legends of Amberland: The Forgotten Crown</a></li><li>low-poly 风格坦克大战 <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/1009200/Tanks_on_the_Eastern_Front/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">Tanks on the Eastern Front</a></li><li>踢足球模拟器 <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/1046230/Soccer_Player_Simulator/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">Soccer Player Simulator</a></li><li>支持移动端和 PC 一起玩的赛车竞速游戏 <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/676960/Hotlap_Heroes/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">Hotlap Heroes</a></li></ul><p>最近朋友们不是在玩只狼就是在玩 baba！baba 真好玩，玩到想变成 keke（语无伦次）</p><p><iframe frameborder="no" border="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" width="100%" height="200" src="https://indienova.com/widget/gamedb/list/91"></iframe></p><h4>Magnibox</h4><p>关键词：益智、解谜</p><p>发售日期：3月26日</p><p>磁铁方块！利用地图上的不同方块和磁力解开谜题。不用为解锁关卡和卡关担心——所有的关卡随便游玩！</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/03/pic-3706WY-Magnibox.gif" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="12318" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/999410/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe></p><h4>Where the Bees Make Honey</h4><p>关键词：心理、解谜</p><p>发售日期：3月26日</p><p>这个标题让我想到 Where the water tastes like wine 了…游戏以一个成年人的视角讲述对童年的回忆与思考，以一些有趣的关卡来带你回味主角 Sunny 的童年。游戏暂无中文。</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/03/pic-4839di-Where_the_Bees_Make_Honey.gif" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="12319" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/03/pic-5030H8-Where_the_Bees_Make_Honey2.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="12320" data-result="success" style="width: 76.02%;" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/1001640/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe></p><h4>StoneTide: Age of Pirates</h4><p>关键词：冒险、生存工艺、在线多人</p><p>发售日期：3月26日（EA）</p><p>体验一把海盗人生！造船、征召船员，惊险刺激的海战、岛屿探索、在线竞技等着你！游戏暂无中文，EA 阶段貌似 bug 还比较多，建议观望。</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/03/pic-5285YY-StoneTide_Age_of_Pirates1.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="12321" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/03/pic-5291zp-StoneTide_Age_of_Pirates2.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="12322" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/1039350/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe></p><h4>Haramatia</h4><p>关键词：冒险、生存</p><p>发售日期：3月28日（EA）</p><p>在失落文明的城镇中生存、探索、交易，随着剧情慢慢寻回自身的记忆，了解这颗星球在被毁灭前发生的事情。游戏暂无中文。</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/03/pic-5582qp-Haramatia1.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="12323" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/03/pic-5591i5-Haramatia2.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="12324" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/1049840/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe><br></p><h4>Willowbrooke Post</h4><p>关键词：模拟、经营</p><p>发售日期：3月28日（EA）</p><p>因故外出的父母将邮局托付给你，你能用有限的时间和资金经营好这个城镇的社交中心吗？投递包裹、贴邮票、写信、记账，你愿意的话也可以给居民们做点小菜！游戏暂无中文，EA 版本 bug 较多，建议观望~</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/03/pic-5947zq-Willowbrooke_Post1.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="12325" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/03/pic-5958id-Willowbrooke_Post2.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="12326" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/938500/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe></p><h4>Pilot Unknown</h4><p>关键词：程序生成、永久死亡</p><p>发售日期：3月28日</p><p>定制你的哨兵船，探索外星地牢！在六边形的战斗池中迎击敌人，探索迷宫、在商店交易、击破 boss。解锁150种收集品、12种武器、遍历7个地牢！游戏暂无中文。</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/03/pic-6452Nu-Pilot_Unknown.gif" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="12327" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/1032570/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe><br></p><h4>The World Next Door</h4><p>关键词：三消、冒险、剧情</p><p>发售日期：3月28日</p><p>在棋盘上用三消攻击对方，同时灵活闪避对方的攻击！少年 Jun 以外来到了一个充满奇妙生物的神秘世界，在时间耗尽前，他得靠着这些有趣的新伙伴和魔法符文回到地球！本作被选入2019 PAX East indie megabooth 的列表中，值得期待！游戏暂无中文。</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/03/pic-4607Fz-The_World_Next_Door1.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="12338" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/03/pic-4643nB-The_World_Next_Door2.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="12339" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/03/pic-4652fa-The_World_Next_Door3.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="12340" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/755470/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe><br></p><h4>Metaloid : Origin</h4><p>关键词：快节奏、平台、射击</p><p>发售日期：3月28日</p><p>不小心把本作标题看成密特罗德了……扮演“掠夺者”机械战士，冲破九个大关，从 Lucian 大军的统治下拯救他们的星球，夺回宝贵的燃料资源！可选三个主角（都是机娘，其中一位还有猫耳……），收集解锁更多强力道具！</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/03/pic-5751s1-Metaloid_Origin1.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="12341" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/03/pic-5760oT-Metaloid_Origin2.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="12342" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/03/pic-5767we-Metaloid_Origin3.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="12343" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/974390/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe><br></p><h4>Curious Cases</h4><p>关键词：推理、解谜</p><p>发售日期：3月29日</p><p>一位科学家声称他的项目得出了突破性的结论，但随即就失踪了！他的办公室大门紧锁，没有任何出入的迹象。这很快引起了警探的注意，他希望像过往一样去处理案件，却发现这次的情况变得有些奇怪……游戏支持最多六人同时解谜，也有专为多人解谜开发的游戏模式！支持 VR 显示，暂无中文。</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/03/pic-60742P-Curious_Cases1.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="12344" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/03/pic-6079Ad-Curious_Cases2.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="12345" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/1045080/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe><br></p><h4>The Puppet of Tersa</h4><p>关键词：点击、冒险、解谜</p><p>发售日期：3月29日</p><p>是什么让 Cynthia 来到这个怪诞世界，阻止她回家呢？探索 Tersa 的世界，在五个章节中探索世界，解开各种谜题，推进剧情，在手绘风的场景下感受孩子的纯真，和世界的黑暗面。游戏暂无中文。</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/03/pic-6561Cy-The_Puppet_of_Tersa1.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="12346" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/03/pic-65726F-The_Puppet_of_Tersa2.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="12347" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/668780/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe><br></p><h4>Rules of The Mafia: Trade &amp; Blood</h4><p>关键词：策略、管理</p><p>发售日期：3月29日</p><p>做一个小市民很容易（哥谭市除外），但成为一个黑手党家族的头头呢？你的目标是控制贸易、赌博、风俗，成为城市的市长。准确分配兵力和资源，稳固自己的地位！对抗其他派系和地下组织，谁能阻止你成为最酷的人？</p><p>游戏没标中文支持，不过商店和日志都是中文的，大概很快也会有中文了~</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/03/pic-69147P-Rules_of_The_Mafia1.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="12348" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/03/pic-6925Bt-Rules_of_The_Mafia2.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="12349" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/03/pic-6929Yq-Rules_of_The_Mafia3.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="12350" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/996830/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe><br></p><h4>The White Laboratory 白色实验室</h4><p>关键词：策略、塔防、即时策略</p><p>发售日期：3月29日</p><p>国人作品，作者一个人开发了10年！本作是一款基于真实物理模拟的沙盒式塔防即时策略游戏。灵活组装零件并布置你的防御塔结构，在大气开采设施上执行维护任务。玩家的基地将会不断受到来自四周敌人的侵袭，击败敌人，利用敌人的“碎块”重构防御塔、拼装螺旋桨空中探机、牵引收集零散碎片……根据物理规则来决定你的战略决策。</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/03/pic-7253Vi-The_White_Laboratory1.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="12351" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/03/pic-7272FR-The_White_Laboratory3.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="12353" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/03/pic-7261fd-The_White_Laboratory2.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="12352" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/235520/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe><br></p><h4>Bugs Must Die 银河除虫队</h4><p>关键词：双摇杆射击</p><p>发售日期：3月29日</p><p>本作灵感来源于《赤色要塞》。玩家做为银河联邦的秘密特工，登陆 M-79行星，驾驶满载武器的战车，与星球上成群结队的螳螂人战士战斗，击溃疯狂科学家制造出的超级 BOSS，推翻他们在 M-79行星上建立的邪恶政权。不同水平的玩家能在不同难度模式中都享受到游戏乐趣。游戏支持中文。</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/03/pic-52687j-GIF_4_clip.gif" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="12354" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/03/pic-5295B8-Bugs_Must_Die_02.gif" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="12355" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/816720/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe><br></p><h4>Bedtime Blues</h4><p>关键词：惊悚</p><p>发售日期：3月30日</p><p>当儿童的无边想象力变成噩梦会如何？儿时爱不释手的泰迪熊活了过来，手里拿着刀……</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/03/pic-5487H5-Bedtime_Blues1.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="12356" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/03/pic-5494FO-Bedtime_Blues2.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="12357" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/966540/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe></p><h4>Blind Souls</h4><p>关键词：步行模拟、唯美</p><p>发售日期：3月30日</p><p>一名中世纪的画家神秘死亡，玩家要帮助她的灵魂完成她生前没能画出的作品。通过已离世之人的眼睛看世界会是怎样的呢？游戏支持中文。</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/03/pic-5735TR-Blind_Souls1.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="12358" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/03/pic-5746HK-Blind_Souls2.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="12359" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/872490/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe></p><h4>Uriel’s Chasm 3: Gelshock</h4><p>关键词：NES、策略</p><p>发售日期：3月30日</p><p>探索深海采矿场，是什么打破了秩序？游戏包含两种模式，使用骰子探索地图，在弹幕战中击破 boss。游戏暂无中文。</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/03/pic-6020c2-Uriel’s_Chasm_3-1.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="12360" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/03/pic-6029lE-Uriel’s_Chasm_3-2.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="12361" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2019/03/pic-6401us-Uriel’s_Chasm_3-3.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="12362" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/1050730/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe></p>
            </div>
        </article>
